Build Shift Crypto's software, packages, and firmware

Tested, functional, and expected to produce builds on these platforms:

  Ubuntu Xenial
  Debian Stretch

Install Docker:

  make install-docker

Build everything:

  make

Selectively build smaller pieces with other Makefile targets.

  Create the base container:

    make build-world

  Build the DBBv1 firmware:

    make build-mcu

  Build the BitBox Wallet application packages for X86_64 GNU/Linux:

    make build-bitbox-wallet-app

  Build the 2fa Android package:

    make build-2fa

